<title>HONG KONG: Far East Aluminium posts loss in year net.</title>
<headline>Far East Aluminium posts loss in year net.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-05-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year ended December 31</p>
<p>(in million HK$ unless stated)</p>
<p>    Shr (H.K. cents)	   10.16 loss  vs  0.62 gain</p>
<p>    Dividend (H.K. cents)    nil	   vs  nil</p>
<p>    Exceptional items	  30.79 gain  vs  1.51 loss</p>
<p>    Net			    30.63 loss  vs  1.87 profit</p>
<p>    Turnover		     231.11	vs  367.80</p>
<p>    Company name		 Far East Aluminium (Holdings) Ltd</p>
<p>    Books close		  N/A</p>
<p>    Dividend payable	   N/A</p>
<p>NOTE - Far East Aluminium is a curtain wall and aluminium works contractor.</p>
<p>The exceptional items in the current year arose from the writing back of the group's share of accumulated losses of associated companies of approximately HK$67.9 million after netting off the full provision of the group's cost of investment in and advance to the associated companies of approximately HK$37.1 million as a result of a change in the nature of the group's interest in the associated companies as more fully described in the section on &quot;Business Review and Recent Developments&quot; in the results announcement.</p>
<p>Total dividend for the year is nil vs one H.K. cent.</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong newsroom (852) 2843 6368</p>
